## ObjectFromEntries type

Turns this:

```ts
type E = [
 ['keyA', 'valueA'],
 ['keyB', 'valueB'],
 ['keyC', 'valueC'],
]
```
Into this:

```ts
type O = {
 keyA: "valueA",
 keyB: "valueB",
 keyC: "valueC",
}
```

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type ObjectFromEntries<T> = T extends ReadonlyArray<any> ? KindaPretty<UnionToIntersection<EntriesToRecordTuple<T>[number]>> : never;
```
**References:** [KindaPretty](./data-schema.kindapretty.md)<!-- -->, [UnionToIntersection](./data-schema.uniontointersection.md)<!-- -->, [EntriesToRecordTuple](./data-schema.entriestorecordtuple.md)
